共狗，必須將佢成個集團所有分身清除，否則連登必死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123735</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcpCtDj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcpCtDj.png&h=d95fea7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaEZGYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaEZGYj.png&h=6e12e1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j8uMrdt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj8uMrdt.png&h=9e16340d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙皮狗一吠，所有連登手足便都指著牠笑，有的叫道，「沙皮狗，站務台又見到你罪證了！」他不回答，自言自語，「老鳳洗板，舉報佢開分身。」便開post亂鳩咁屈。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又開了奶共的post了！」沙皮狗睜大眼睛吠，「你怎麼這樣憑空污狗清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你開了奶共post，被追擊。」沙皮狗便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯吠，「文匯大公不能算奶共&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公！&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公報的事，能算奶共麼？」接連便是難懂的嗚咽聲，什麼「老鳳推人去死」，什麼「老鳳俾我迫到傻咗」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</span></span>"},{"pid":"f2900172a1724023e9b8d84a3a6d03038855461d","tid":2290630,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T15:52:09.000Z","msg":"頭先有手足係天水圍叫完「光復香港，時代革命」口號後墜樓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aFCqxzV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aFCqxzV</a><br />\n#87 回覆<br />\n<br />\n吉acc"},{"pid":"3972d6795b650b923c9e71c6655371c1f4aaa292","tid":2290630,"uid":146642,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2e576194eb8e4b84522f618ca1809ab1dd78abc0","tid":2290630,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:17:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T08:53:20.000Z","msg":"老鳳殺狗未？"},{"pid":"e540bcab2128287fdf9fb162955b42af00f424a7","tid":2290630,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1285f569b1f1b313123e98ed972b82c3da7f4bdb","tid":2290630,"uid":